<body>
  <% content_for :title do %>Coder Day of Service by CodeMontage<% end %>
  <div class="mlkday">
    <div id="mlk_welcome" class="ten columns centered">
      <%=image_tag image_path("logos/CDS-horiz-logo.jpg") %>
      <p>On January 18, a diverse group of over 200 coders inspired by Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. gathered in NYC and online to contribute to <strong>open source, social impact</strong> projects. Keynotes by technology leaders <strong><%= link_to "Julie Ann Horvath", "http://storify.com/CodeMontage/julie-ann-horvath-coder-day-of-service-keynote" %></strong> and <strong><%= link_to "John Resig", "http://storify.com/CodeMontage/john-resig-coder-day-of-service-keynote" %></strong> set the tone for collaboration, and more than <strong><%= link_to "50 projects", projects_path %></strong> were amplified that day.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div id="mlkd_video" class="flex-video">
      <iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/85846616?byline=0&amp;color=ffffff" width="500" height="281" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>
      <p><a href="http://vimeo.com/85846616">Coder Day of Service, powered by CodeMontage</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/codemontage">CodeMontage</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="mlkd_sponsors" class="row">
      <div class="ten columns centered">
        <h2>Coder Day of Service January 2014 Sponsors</h2>
        <div class="sponsors row centered">
          <% @sponsors.each do |featured| %>
            <div class="four columns">
                <h5>
                <% if find_logo?(featured) %>
                  <%= link_to (image_tag find_logo(featured)), organization_path(featured) %>
                <% else %>
                  <%= link_to featured.name, organization_path(featured) %>
                <% end %>
                </h5>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <% content_for(:press) do %>Press<% end %>
</body>
